description:
After Jesus' temptation in the wilderness, he returned to his hometown, where he did not experience a heroic welcome home. They questioned Jesus' mission and identity and ran him out of the city, trying to kill him. Jesus showed at the start that whether people loved or hated him, his mission stayed the same.
